{"type": "article", "id": 45771, "title": "想要营造平和的空间？来看看这些柔和色搭配｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2017-10-07T23:04:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 435, "name": "室内设计"}, {"id": 44474, "name": "The New Design Project"}, {"id": 44475, "name": "Dan Gayfer Design"}, {"id": 44476, "name": "Grzywinsi+Pons"}, {"id": 44477, "name": "HelgessonGonzaga Arkitekter"}, {"id": 44478, "name": "Studio Sur Rue"}, {"id": 44479, "name": "Nimtim"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 476, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170930161255rfGKMDb5RpHzWvx0.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p>去年，我们曾在<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/32318.html\">文章</a>中分析过 2016 年度色彩“粉晶”和“静谧蓝”是如何因时局的动荡不安而变得流行，用柔和的力量给人带去安慰。如果你也向往拥有一个采用柔和色的庇护所，不妨来看看下面这几个案例。</p><h3>Fresh and Serene by The New Design Project</h3><p>当客户提出希望可以“不过分强调设计感”、“打开门就能有家的温暖感”时，纽约设计工作室 <a href=\"https://thenewdesignproject.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">The New Design Project</a> 想到了用柔和色来中和黑白的做法。在这座位于曼哈顿的公寓内，淡淡的蓝、绿、灰结合在一起，平衡了一些黑色和金色家居营造出的奢华感，让人很容易感受到整个空间的清新和宁静，而浴室中米色瓷砖和灰白色浮云壁纸的搭配则像是一个隐藏的惊喜。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709301613488fxiMebUHIZo3uzB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161348BOSkM7Amjc0RpyFv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161348aLIhBic5kKHtj7zC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497066\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161349ARG1rHvjNYpt7T35.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>High House by Dan Gayfer Design</h3><p>只要搭配合理，在不常选择的地方铺上瓷砖也能带来意想不到的效果。这间里外都点缀了大量瓷砖的小屋出自墨尔本工作室 <a href=\"http://dangayfer.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dan Gayfer Design</a> 之手，一楼厨房使用的瓷砖刚好与岛台侧面的相呼应，二楼主卧和儿童卧室的两个阳台则分别铺设了蓝色与粉色的瓷砖，相同的配置也出现在了上下两间浴室之中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161331Wr9PYZIRVLuB8gqN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.282051\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161331pAVeRz63QOuB17Iy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714744\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161331E1QmFUT2ZOMcNG5A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714744\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161331ugk1UGFbqL0A2IQj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714744\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161332kZ5rMj8qxVvIGEHm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714744\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Urban Villa hotel by Grzywinsi+Pons</h3><p>如果你偏好不那么冷峻的工业风，下次去伦敦时可以去由纽约工作室 <a href=\"http://gp-arch.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Grzywinsi+Pons</a> 设计的 Urban Villa 酒店坐坐。<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/34387.html\">擅长玩混搭</a>的设计团队在酒吧区域设置了绿色屏风、绿植墙，并且大量采用柔和色的简约风家具，它们和淡色木地板和天花板一道，营造出一种自然纯朴的氛围。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161403y2BtAaoE5b3jU1gm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.852564\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161403JjVGyUZ9nAPX138C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.029915\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161403iYakJNQDh3Sd0tns.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.854701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>House 669 by HelgessonGonzaga Arkitekter</h3><p>这座位于斯德哥尔摩的双层小屋是不是让你想起了小时候随手画下的房子？有着黄色框架的门和大小不一的窗户让灰色的外墙变得柔和不少，但也不会太过张扬。操刀设计的建筑事务所 <a href=\"http://www.helgessongonzaga.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">HelgessonGonzaga Arkitekter</a> 在一楼就使用了淡黄、蓝绿、紫和红四种颜色，在区分不同空间的同时，营造出活泼感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161419txwnKpGEQgauPe1O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.768779\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161418P029yc7R6eW5mVXr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.768779\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161418rN3GUIpcZBjnyl2Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.299883\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161418bhrqWQ4fSaGnv2Cy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.768779\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Yafo by Studio Sur Rue</h3><p>如果不是踏进 Yafo 熟食店确认过菜单和柜台上的食物，你很有可能将这个大面积使用粉色的空间当作是一家小清新甜品店。在为这家专营以色列菜的熟食店出谋划策之前，法国工作室 <a href=\"http://studio-sur-rue.fr/index.php/category/projets/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studio Sur Rue</a> 特意观摩了主厨 Lahmi 的料理方式以获取灵感。为了缓和粉色带来的甜腻感，地板、门框和立柱都采用了沉稳的墨绿。值得一提的是，所有餐具都直接收纳在厨房上方的不锈钢架内，配合那些柔和色的托盘，在这里俯拍出一张好看的美食照似乎并不难。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709301615339qGoRbNs81t2THOr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664319\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161534JOSNXAjuIVLW46pT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161533YtOk623GiBQDFueb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161533o0fY9vH4ItCJMcbA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500587\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>London flat by Nimtim</h3><p>由英国工作室 <a href=\"http://www.nimtim.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nimtim</a> 负责改造的这间 45 平米一室户属于一名常在三地间奔波、不太长住的儿童心外科医生，她的诉求是希望可以在难得回家休息时尽可能地感到安心和放松。为此，Nimtim 的设计团队在开放式的厨房和客厅配置了漆成淡蓝、搭配金色门把的橱柜，沿着木地板走进藏在背后的卧室，木衣柜将暖色调延伸到了墙壁，缓和了蓝色墙壁带来的冷感。除此之外，客厅里的明黄色扶手椅和红色衣架也有点亮整个空间的效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161444fZCOVDQJzNEI8uKj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662393\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161444YO8WIQbr3KNFETd2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452991\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930161444R21r4mIdzCJ7jM6F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714744\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}